version_description: Simple way to play the song on acoustic guitar.

song_name: I Cant Go On Without You

version_description: This version has chords and lyrics - perfect if you are playing rhythm guitar. If you're looking for a tab of the main riff, intro/outro, etc., then check one of the existing versions. Copped the chords from this video: https://youtu.be/qMDq4CGckW4.
The absence of chords of the Kaleo version of Vor i Vaglaskogi was odd so the original was adapted to fit the Kaleo cover. A novice song, but a very emotional one with a haunting melody.
This is a fingerpicking version of Vor i Vaglaskogi combining chords with the riffs and the "solo". For the original version this tab is based on check https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ABx6Zdl1aIQ.
Includes intro tab and simplified chords.
Chords for the whole song / based on "Live in a Volcano" / https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9WIU5NN1Q0g.

performance.name: Live in a Volcano
performance.comment: Kaleo shot a live performance of the song inside Þríhnúkagígur volcano in Iceland. It's the only volcano in the world you can explore. It hasn't errupted in about 4,000 years.

version_description: Capo on the 4th instead of the 1st. Variation in chords. Lyrics. https://youtu.be/UGEKSH--BC0.

Played this on acoustic guitar sounded close to the original, not exact but sounds fairly good. Not certain but if you use these chords and your guitar tuned half-step down without a capo you might sound just like the original. But tried this and it worked hope everyone likes it. Please leave comments if you have suggestions and please rate.
